  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A rosette of magic resembling a dandelion of energy appears in your hand. The magical flower remains there for the duration. When you cast this spell, you blow gently on the rosette, sending a stream of glowing seeds at a creature you can see within 60 feet of you. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 3d6 radiant damage. Until the spell ends, you can blow on the rosette and make the attack again on each of your turns as an action.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 2nd.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
